### ============== PUBLIC MENU ROUTES ==============

### 1. Get All Menus (Basic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get All Menus with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 3. Filter by Vendor Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?vendorCategory=home_chef
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 4. Filter by Cuisine
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?cuisine=indian
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 5. Filter by Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500
